        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>21st Century NICS Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies provisions governing the national instant criminal background check system (NICS).</p> <p>Specifically, it permits the NICS to query an additional database&#8212;the National Data Exchange&#8212;as part of a firearm-related background check.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
